n.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/T%C3%ADch-hoa/poem-OyPgnjg3EcvtCt6tBgYaXw">Tích hoa - 惜花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Ti%E1%BA%BFn-kinh-tri%E1%BB%81u-y%E1%BA%BFt-ng%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B7-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-YXtVOELHELG4-k6r56WoAA">Tiến kinh triều yết ngật kỷ sự - 進京朝謁訖紀事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nghi-T%C3%B4n/Tu%C3%BD-B%E1%BB%93ng-Lai/poem-YiGy0Yobn2xQlPWYtO-Amg">Tuý Bồng Lai - 醉蓬萊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nghi-T%C3%B4n/author-pd7XsJJghP2Tos8AhibgnQ">Vương Nghi Tôn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-mai/poem-m60tKVQoonnoG6CkMWHQiw">Vịnh mai - 詠梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
